#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" A top choice for floral needs. <br/>Elegant designs, excellent service, "
"and lasting beauty. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ທາງເລືອກອັນດັບໜຶ່ງສຳລັບເລື່ອງດອກໄມ້. <br/>ການອອກແບບທີ່ສະຫງ່າງາມ, ການບໍລິການທີ່ດີເລີດ, ແລະ "
"ຄວາມງາມທີ່ຄົງທົນ. \""

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Exceptional flowers and service! <br/>They make every occasion special "
"and memorable. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ດອກໄມ້ ແລະ ການບໍລິການທີ່ດີເຍື້ຍມ! <br/>ພວກເຂົາເຮັດໃຫ້ທຸກໆໂອກາດກາຍເປັນສິ່ງທີ່ພິເສດ ແລະ "
"ໜ້າຈົດຈຳ. \""

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Their arrangements are stunning. Fresh, creative, and always beautifully "
"crafted. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ການຈັດດອກໄມ້ຂອງພວກເຂົາແມ່ນສວຍງາມຫຼາຍ. ມີຄວາມສົດໃໝ່, ສ້າງສັນ, ແລະ "
"ຖືກອອກແບບມາຢ່າງປະນີດສະເໝີ. \""

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_framed_intro
msgid ""
"<a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-lg btn-secondary o_translate_inline\">See the "
"Full Bloom</a>"
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-lg btn-secondary "
"o_translate_inline\">ເບິ່ງດອກໄມ້ທີ່ເບັ່ງບານເຕັມທີ່</a>"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_text_image
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Deliver flowers to live up to your dedication for your loved ones."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        ສົ່ງມອບດອກໄມ້ເພື່ອສະແດງເຖິງຄວາມຕັ້ງໃຈຂອງທ່ານທີ່ມີຕໍ່ຄົນທີ່ທ່ານຮັກ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<br/>Creating vibrant, handcrafted bouquets to celebrate every occasion.<br/"
"><br/>"
msgstr "<br/>ສ້າງສັນຊໍ່ດອກໄມ້ທີ່ມີສີສັນສົດໃສ ແລະ ປະນີດ ເພື່ອສະເຫຼີມສະຫຼອງໃນທຸກໆໂອກາດ.<br/><br/>"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" role=\"img\"/>  Fresh "
"and beautiful"
msgstr ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" role=\"img\"/>  ສົດໃໝ່ ແລະ "
"ສວຍງາມ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_title
msgid "A Deep Dive into Blooms and Beauty"
msgstr "ເຈາະເລິກເຖິງຄວາມເບັ່ງບານ ແລະ ຄວາມສວຍງາມ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"A delicate blend of soft pink roses and baby's breath, perfect for "
"expressing love and gratitude."
msgstr ""
"ການປະສົມປະສານທີ່ອ່ອນໂຍນຂອງດອກກຸຫຼາບສີຊົມພູອ່ອນ ແລະ ດອກເບບີ້ບຣີດ (baby's breath), "
"ເໝາະສຳລັບການສະແດງຄວາມຮັກ ແລະ ຄວາມຂອບໃຈ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_hexagonal
msgid "A place of paradise for flower lovers"
msgstr "ສະຖານທີ່ແຫ່ງສະຫວັນສຳລັບຄົນຮັກດອກໄມ້"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"A small shop with a very large selection of roses. Nice prices and above all "
"a very professional and friendly welcome."
msgstr ""
"ຮ້ານນ້ອຍໆທີ່ມີດອກກຸຫຼາບໃຫ້ເລືອກຫຼາຍຢ່າງ. ລາຄາເປັນກັນເອງ ແລະ ທີ່ສຳຄັນແມ່ນການຕ້ອນຮັບທີ່ເປັນມືອາຊີບ ແລະ "
"ເປັນມິດຫຼາຍ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"A wide range of high quality products and a warm welcome! I recommend this "
"shop 200%!"
msgstr "ມີສິນຄ້າຄຸນນະພາບສູງໃຫ້ເລືອກຫຼາກຫຼາຍ ແລະ ການຕ້ອນຮັບທີ່ອົບອຸ່ນ! ຂ້ອຍແນະນຳຮ້ານນີ້ເລີຍ 200%!"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_framed_intro
msgid "About Us"
msgstr "ກ່ຽວກັບພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Aline Turner, Bouquet Designer"
msgstr "Aline Turner, ນັກອອກແບບຊໍ່ດອກໄມ້"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Aline is the mastermind behind our bespoke floral arrangements."
msgstr "Aline ແມ່ນຜູ້ນຳຫຼັກໃນການສ້າງສັນການຈັດດອກໄມ້ຕາມສັ່ງຂອງພວກເຮົາ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"As we use local growers, our flowers last longer and smell better. Just like "
"the event you want to celebrate with flowers!"
msgstr ""
"ເນື່ອງຈາກພວກເຮົາໃຊ້ດອກໄມ້ຈາກຜູ້ປູກໃນທ້ອງຖິ່ນ, ດອກໄມ້ຂອງພວກເຮົາຈຶ່ງສົດໄດ້ດົນກວ່າ ແລະ ມີກິ່ນຫອມກວ່າ. "
"ຄືກັນກັບງານລ້ຽງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການສະເຫຼີມສະຫຼອງດ້ວຍດອກໄມ້!"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_three_columns
msgid "Bio Flowers"
msgstr "ດອກໄມ້ອໍແກນິກ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_unveil
msgid "Bloom with Elegance"
msgstr "ເບັ່ງບານດ້ວຍຄວາມສະຫງ່າງາມ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.configurator_s_kickoff
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_framed_intro
msgid "Bloom with Joy:"
msgstr "ເບັ່ງບານດ້ວຍຄວາມສຸກ:"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_cards_grid
msgid "Blooming with Quality and Care"
msgstr "ເບັ່ງບານດ້ວຍຄຸນນະພາບ ແລະ ຄວາມໃສ່ໃຈ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_carousel_intro
msgid "Blooming with elegance and beauty"
msgstr "ເບັ່ງບານດ້ວຍຄວາມສະຫງ່າງາມ ແລະ ສວຍງາມ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Blushing Harmony"
msgstr "ຄວາມກົມກຽວທີ່ອ່ອນຫວານ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.configurator_s_image_text_overlap
msgid ""
"Brighten any corner of the globe with our express 24-hour worldwide flower "
"delivery service."
msgstr "ສ້າງຄວາມສົດໃສໃຫ້ກັບທຸກມຸມໂລກ ດ້ວຍບໍລິການສົ່ງດອກໄມ້ດ່ວນທົ່ວໂລກພາຍໃນ 24 ຊົ່ວໂມງຂອງພວກເຮົາ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_empowerment
msgid "Brighten your day with<br/>stunning designs from your local florist"
msgstr "ເຮັດໃຫ້ມື້ຂອງທ່ານສົດໃສດ້ວຍ<br/>ການອອກແບບທີ່ສວຍງາມຈາກຮ້ານດອກໄມ້ໃນທ້ອງຖິ່ນຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_striped_center_top
msgid "Bring Nature to Your Space"
msgstr "ນຳທຳມະຊາດມາສູ່ພື້ນທີ່ຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quadrant
msgid ""
"Bring nature’s beauty into your life with our exquisite floral arrangements "
"and garden designs. Our selections are perfect for any occasion and setting."
"<br/><br/> Discover the elegance of flowers and greenery."
msgstr ""
"ນຳຄວາມງາມຂອງທຳມະຊາດມາສູ່ຊີວິດຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍການຈັດດອກໄມ້ ແລະ ການອອກແບບສວນທີ່ປະນີດ. "
"ສິ່ງທີ່ພວກເຮົາຄັດສັນມາແມ່ນເໝາະສຳລັບທຸກໂອກາດ ແລະ ທຸກສະຖານທີ່.<br/><br/> "
"ຄົ້ນພົບຄວາມສະຫງ່າງາມຂອງດອກໄມ້ ແລະ ພື້ນທີ່ສີຂຽວ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_card_offset
msgid "Bringing Nature to Your Doorstep"
msgstr "ນຳທຳມະຊາດມາສົ່ງເຖິງໜ້າບ້ານທ່ານ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid "Bringing the Beauty of Nature to Your Space"
msgstr "ນຳຄວາມງາມຂອງທຳມະຊາດມາສູ່ພື້ນທີ່ຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quadrant
msgid "Browse Flowers"
msgstr "ເລືອກເບິ່ງດອກໄມ້"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"Browse our floral arrangements   <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\" "
"role=\"img\"/>"
msgstr ""
"ເລືອກເບິ່ງການຈັດດອກໄມ້ຂອງພວກເຮົາ   <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\" "
"role=\"img\"/>"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_card_offset
msgid "Celebrate nature’s beauty with us."
msgstr "ຮ່ວມສະເຫຼີມສະຫຼອງຄວາມງາມຂອງທຳມະຊາດໄປກັບພວກເຮົາ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Celebrate with Our Best-Selling Bouquets, perfect for every occasion."
msgstr "ສະເຫຼີມສະຫຼອງດ້ວຍຊໍ່ດອກໄມ້ທີ່ຂາຍດີທີ່ສຸດຂອງພວກເຮົາ, ເໝາະສຳລັບທຸກໂອກາດ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Classic Rose Bouquet"
msgstr "ຊໍ່ດອກກຸຫຼາບແບບຄລາສສິກ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Comprehensive floral decoration service for events including weddings, "
"parties, and corporate gatherings, designed to enhance your venue."
msgstr ""
"ບໍລິການຕົກແຕ່ງດອກໄມ້ຄົບວົງຈອນສຳລັບງານຕ່າງໆ ລວມທັງງານແຕ່ງດອງ, ງານລ້ຽງ, ແລະ "
"ງານສັງສັນຂອງບໍລິສັດ, ອອກແບບມາເພື່ອເພີ່ມຄວາມສວຍງາມໃຫ້ກັບສະຖານທີ່ຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_striped_center_top
msgid "Crafted with nature’s finest"
msgstr "ສ້າງສັນດ້ວຍສິ່ງທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດຈາກທຳມະຊາດ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_cards_grid
msgid "Creativity Like a Wildflower"
msgstr "ຄວາມສ້າງສັນດັ່ງດອກໄມ້ປ່າ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_benefits
msgid "Custom Floral Arrangements"
msgstr "ການຈັດດອກໄມ້ແບບພິເສດ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Custom Floral Design"
msgstr "ການອອກແບບດອກໄມ້ຕາມຄວາມຕ້ອງການ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_wavy_grid
msgid "Customized Bouquets"
msgstr "ຊໍ່ດອກໄມ້ທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງໄດ້ເອງ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_benefits
msgid "Dedicated Service"
msgstr "ການບໍລິການດ້ວຍຄວາມຕັ້ງໃຈ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_images_mosaic
msgid "Discover Our Latest Floral Arrangements"
msgstr "ຄົ້ນພົບການຈັດດອກໄມ້ໃໝ່ລ່າສຸດຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Discover Our Most Loved Arrangements"
msgstr "ຄົ້ນພົບການຈັດດອກໄມ້ທີ່ເປັນທີ່ນິຍົມທີ່ສຸດ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_shape_image
msgid ""
"Discover our exquisite floral arrangements for any occasion. From vibrant "
"bouquets to elegant centerpieces, we craft each design with care, using "
"fresh, beautiful flowers to brighten your day and celebrate life's moments."
msgstr ""
"ຄົ້ນພົບການຈັດດອກໄມ້ທີ່ປະນີດຂອງພວກເຮົາສຳລັບທຸກໂອກາດ. "
